text: Mukhamadmurod Abdurakhmonov (born November 29, 1986) is a Tajikistani judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's +100 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the first round by Alex García Mendoza. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Tajikistani male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Tajikistan Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Judoka at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Tajikistan
